auth {
  mode: bearer
}

auth:bearer {
  token: {{apiKey}}
}

docs {
  # Edgecute Backtest API — automated tests

  Collection-level auth sends `Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}` on every request
  whose auth mode is `inherit`. Negative auth tests override this with `auth: none`.

  Run with `./run.sh` (boots the API with the deterministic demo facade, mints a
  sandbox key, runs the suite) — see README.md.
}
